dct_title_s: A map of the most inhabited part of Virginia : containing the whole province of Maryland with part of Pensilvania, New Jersey and North Carolina
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Prime meridians: Philadelphia and London. Dedication: To the Right Honourable, George Dunk Earl of Halifax ... Includes distance chart.
dct_publisher_sm: London : Printed for Robt. Sayer & Thos. Jefferys, [1775]
